308
00:21:30,280 --> 00:21:31,810
- Sedni si.
- Ano.

309
00:21:32,430 --> 00:21:35,200
Najezme se spolu.
Chutná to dobře.

310
00:21:35,200 --> 00:21:36,730
Rámen je...

311
00:21:36,730 --> 00:21:37,780
